|line6=JC中央線快速|left6=四谷|right6=中野|note-left6=JC 04<br />3.7km|note-mid6={{車站編號r|JC|05|#f15a22|1}}<br />距離東京10.3km|note-right6=JC 06<br />4.4km}}
