|上下車人次 = 786,052<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.keio.co.jp/group/traffic/railroading/passengers/|title=1日の駅別乗降人員|publisher=京王グループ|access-date=2013-11-29|archive-date=2013-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130428040718/http://www.keio.co.jp/group/traffic/railroading/passengers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>*
|統計年度 = 2017年
|停站路線數=
|adjacent = {{Adjacent stations|system=京王電鐵|line=京王線|right=笹塚|note-mid={{車站編號r|KO|01|#dd0077|5}}<br />起點|note-right=KO04<br />3.6km}}
|route_map={{Routemap|title=京王新宿站|title-bg=#dd0077|inline=yes|map=
